AvtoVAZ Climbs Most in Two Weeks After Reporting Sales Jump

-- B y   J a s o n   C o r c o r a n
-- 
2011-07-04T15:27:15Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-04/avtovaz-climbs-most-in-two-weeks-after-reporting-sales-jump-1-.html
OAO  AvtoVAZ (AVAZ)  rose the most in two
weeks after the Russian automaker said June vehicle sales
increased 7.9 percent compared with the same month a year
earlier.  The shares rose as much 3.8 percent before closing 2.1
percent higher at 31.516 rubles by 6:45 p.m. in Moscow, their
biggest advance since June 21.  To contact the reporter on this story:
